<plot>In a futuristic society, People called Z-Fighters pilot Mechanical Combat Units known as Zoids. The Young Pilot, R.D. and his Liger ZERO, along with the rest of Team Mach Storm pilot these Zoids into battle against other teams in high speed combat. Some Zoids have special parteners called Fuzor Zoids, and they can fuze with eachother to enhance their power. The newest Zoids Seires has not yet been released in Japan, but it is already a big hit in the United States. Although the Berserk Fury and Liger ZERO from Zoids New Century/Zero have returned, this seires is a totaly new take on the world of Zoids.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?671586</url></doc>
